   - **`extensions/pulseboard/src/runtime-api.ts`** — SDK barrel importing from individual subpaths (no dedicated `openclaw/plugin-sdk/pulseboard` facade):
     ```ts
     export { describeAccountSnapshot } from "openclaw/plugin-sdk/account-helpers";
