   - **`extensions/pulseboard/src/send.ts`** — Stubbed send: records outbound activity, generates message ID `pb-${Date.now()}-${random}`, would POST to `${serverUrl}/api/v1/messages`

   - **`extensions/pulseboard/src/setup-core.ts`** — Setup adapter; maps `ChannelSetupInput` fields: `httpUrl→serverUrl`, `token→apiToken`, `userId→username`; exports `updatePulseboardAccountConfig`, `setPulseboardDmPolicy`, `setPulseboardAllowFrom`, `setPulseboardGroupAccess`, `pulseboardSetupAdapter`

   - **`extensions/pulseboard/src/setup-surface.ts`** — Full wizard with textInputs for serverUrl/token/username/boards, groupAccess, allowFrom, dmPolicy; env var detection; exports `pulseboardSetupWizard`, `pulseboardSetupAdapter`

   - **`extensions/pulseboard/src/channel.ts`** — Main plugin; critical fix: builds `pulseboardMeta: ChannelMeta` inline instead of using `getChatChannelMeta("pulseboard")` (which only works for pre-registered channel IDs). Key sections:
     ```ts
     import type { ChannelMeta } from "openclaw/plugin-sdk/channel-runtime";
     import { createChatChannelPlugin } from "openclaw/plugin-sdk/core";
     const pulseboardMeta: ChannelMeta = {
       id: "pulseboard", label: "PulseBoard", selectionLabel: "PulseBoard (Boards + DMs)",
